{"id":"api/common/DATE_PIPE_DEFAULT_TIMEZONE","title":"DATE_PIPE_DEFAULT_TIMEZONE","contents":"<article>\n  <div class=\"breadcrumb-container\">\n    <div class=\"breadcrumb\">\n      <script type=\"application/ld+json\">\n        {\n          \"@context\": \"http://schema.org\",\n          \"@type\": \"BreadcrumbList\",\n          \"itemListElement\": [\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 1, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.cn/api\", \"name\": \"API\" } },\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 2, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.cn/api/common\", \"name\": \"@angular/common\" } },\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 3, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.cn/api/common/DATE_PIPE_DEFAULT_TIMEZONE\", \"name\": \"DATE_PIPE_DEFAULT_TIMEZONE\" } }\n          ]\n        }\n      </script>\n        <a href=\"/api\">API</a> &gt; <a href=\"api/common\">@angular/common</a>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"github-links\">\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/edit/cn/packages/common/src/pipes/date_pipe.ts?message=docs(common)%3A%20請簡述你的修改...#L30-L29\" aria-label=\"提供編輯建議\" title=\"提供編輯建議\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">mode_edit</i></a>\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/tree/16.1.0-next.3/packages/common/src/pipes/date_pipe.ts#L30-L29\" aria-label=\"檢視原始碼\" title=\"檢視原始碼\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">code</i></a>\n</div>\n  </div>\n  <header ng-should-translate=\"\" class=\"api-header\">\n    <h1 id=\"date_pipe_default_timezone\">DATE_PIPE_DEFAULT_TIMEZONE<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/common/DATE_PIPE_DEFAULT_TIMEZONE#date_pipe_default_timezone\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h1>\n    <label class=\"api-type-label const\">const</label>\n    <label class=\"api-status-label deprecated\">已棄用</label>\n  </header>\n  <aio-toc class=\"embedded\"></aio-toc>\n\n  <div class=\"api-body\">\n  <section ng-should-translate=\"\" class=\"short-description\">\n    <p translation-result=\"on\">用於所有 <code><a href=\"api/common/DatePipe\" class=\"code-anchor\">DatePipe</a></code> 例項的（可選）提供的預設時區（例如 <code>'+0430'</code>）。如果未提供該值，則\n<code><a href=\"api/common/DatePipe\" class=\"code-anchor\">DatePipe</a></code> 將使用終端使用者的本地系統時區。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Optionally-provided default timezone to use for all instances of <code><a href=\"api/common/DatePipe\" class=\"code-anchor\">DatePipe</a></code> (such as <code>'+0430'</code>).\nIf the value isn't provided, the <code><a href=\"api/common/DatePipe\" class=\"code-anchor\">DatePipe</a></code> will use the end-user's local system timezone.</p>\n\n\n  </section>\n<section ng-should-translate=\"\" class=\"deprecated\">\n  <p><strong>已棄用:</strong> use DATE_PIPE_DEFAULT_OPTIONS token to configure DatePipe</p>\n<p>使用 DATE_PIPE_DEFAULT_OPTIONS 令牌來配置 DatePipe</p>\n\n</section>\n  <code-example language=\"ts\" hidecopy=\"true\" class=\"no-box api-heading deprecated-api-item\">\n  const <a href=\"api/common/DATE_PIPE_DEFAULT_TIMEZONE\" class=\"code-anchor\">DATE_PIPE_DEFAULT_TIMEZONE</a>: <a href=\"api/core/InjectionToken\" class=\"code-anchor\">InjectionToken</a>&lt;string&gt;;\n  </code-example>\n\n  \n</div>\n</article>\n\n<!-- links to this doc:\n - api/common\n - api/common/DatePipe\n - guide/deprecations\n - guide/update-to-version-15\n-->\n<!-- links from this doc:\n - /api\n - api/common\n - api/common/DATE_PIPE_DEFAULT_TIMEZONE#date_pipe_default_timezone\n - api/common/DatePipe\n - api/core/InjectionToken\n - https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/edit/cn/packages/common/src/pipes/date_pipe.ts?message=docs(common)%3A%20請簡述你的修改...#L30-L29\n - https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/tree/16.1.0-next.3/packages/common/src/pipes/date_pipe.ts#L30-L29\n-->"}